{"tid":2004098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「長大後再回來付錢」 不捨孩子挨餓   東京便當店推抗疫愛心便當","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:10:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec36ee5457175d044e4b3f5af513ddd0fb131bfd","tid":2004098,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"日本因為武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，4月中宣布全國進入緊急狀態，學校也隨之停課，校內免費午餐亦停止供應，造成許多弱勢兒童吃不上飯。東京吉祥寺的長男堂便當店不捨孩子挨餓，推出兒童愛心便當，並表示可以「長大後再來才付錢」，公告一出網友紛紛讚嘆「太感人了」「要哭了，人真好」。<br />\n<br />\n日本於4月16日宣布全國進入緊急狀態，學校也跟著停課，不但有課程銜接的問題，對許多依賴校內免費午餐的孩童來說，不上學等於沒飯吃，位於東京的一家便當店不捨小朋友挨餓，特別推出便宜的特製兒童便當，並在店外張貼公告，歡迎有需要的小朋友來用餐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OgkC_FdMCe0GaNix7I9Y6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTk0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/uQaYMp0BqBrv8p14sS_w0Q--~B/aD02MDA7dz00NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/d96ca29fb2f465628f1e055095f92024\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOgkC_FdMCe0GaNix7I9Y6g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTk0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuQaYMp0BqBrv8p14sS_w0Q--~B%2FaD02MDA7dz00NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fd96ca29fb2f465628f1e055095f92024&h=52058922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（翻攝自twitter @haru_chat）來用餐。<br />\n<br />\n公告寫著，直到學校重新開放之前，在每個星期一、四、五的上午11點30分到下午6點，提供售價250日圓的兒童便當，並且強調「如果你是錢不夠的孩子，你可以晚一點再付。如有需要的話，你可以在長大之後再回來付。如果等到你長大時，長男堂已經關門了，那麼就請用這些錢幫助其他人，或捐給有需要的人。」<br />\n<br />\n有民眾將公告拍下來貼上網路，大讚老闆的善心，網友也紛紛留言表示「真是個好人」「累了一天，聽到這麼溫暖的消息真是太棒了」「感動到想哭」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P.hGZdIScv8FFKrh1uxQ_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNDgyNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/GPSWUSPk8mbNvyt3qgl95w--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/c721d0a856ca4e6b7e56de9ba5ee1dab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FP.hGZdIScv8FFKrh1uxQ_Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNDgyNQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGPSWUSPk8mbNvyt3qgl95w--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fc721d0a856ca4e6b7e56de9ba5ee1dab&h=6ee15f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（翻攝長男堂官網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%BB%98%E9%8C%A2-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8D%A8%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%8C%A8%E9%A4%93%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E4%BE%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83%E4%BE%BF%E7%95%B6-081535288.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%259B%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BB%2598%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258D%25A8%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258C%25A8%25E9%25A4%2593%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6-081535288.html&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBYvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=428e6512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%BB%98%E9%8C%A2-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8D%A8%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%8C%A8%E9%A4%93%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E4%BE%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83%E4%BE%BF%E7%95%B6-081535288.html</a>"},{"pid":"08adad898fa3e5b3e30f1a5ae9558fee6504e706","tid":2004098,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ea4edbeed204dcd68d4da414433380a26be2a0","tid":2004098,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"人間有情"},{"pid":"b37b2c670